{"tid":145354,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[費用全免][DSE]星說 The Renaissance of Stars 2017 Maths Mock大放送!","createTime":"2017-03-06T07:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T06:41:48.000Z","uid":42916,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88fe66b24cf86e31034bca6a9519cbcd2c9caa19","tid":145354,"uid":42916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我賣廣告住 我哋不收分文架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1466507586935287/photos/a.1468875003365212.1073741828.1466507586935287/1806887702897272/?type=3&amp;comment_id=1806962499556459&amp;force_theater=true&amp;notif_t=photo_comment&amp;notif_id=1488770311230090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1466507586935287%2Fphotos%2Fa.1468875003365212.1073741828.1466507586935287%2F1806887702897272%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26comment_id%3D1806962499556459%26force_theater%3Dtrue%26notif_t%3Dphoto_comment%26notif_id%3D1488770311230090&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5e2cb221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1466507586935287/photos/a.1468875003365212.1073741828.1466507586935287/1806887702897272/?type=3&amp;comment_id=1806962499556459&amp;force_theater=true&amp;notif_t=photo_comment&amp;notif_id=1488770311230090</a><br />\n<br />\n《 星說 模擬試數學卷 放送活動！ 》<br />\n為了幫助同學應付2017中學文憑試，星說決定公開本年度的模擬試數學卷予大家作操卷之用！本試卷由星說數學組全力擬定，擬卷成員包括港大精算 及 風險管理學 等等！<br />\n這份數學卷檔案包括了<br />\n1. Paper 1 &amp; Paper 2<br />\n2. Paper 1 Marking Scheme<br />\n3. Paper 2 FULL Solution (有哂每條MC嘅Steps)<br />\n4. Candidates' Performance<br />\n5. Examination Statistics<br />\n如果同學們想獲得這份考卷，就要完成以下活動要求了~<br />\n<br />\n1. Like 星說Page <br />\n2. 在本Facebook post 的留言欄裡 TAG 4位同學<br />\n3. SHARE本Facebook post 到你的 Facebook Wall （請記得調校 Post Privacy 至公開）<br />\n4. INBOX 星說 Page<br />\n<br />\n目前只提供英文版試卷，如果反應良好的話我們會加推中文版試卷給各位同學作操卷之用！<br />\n活動時間為一星期，大家不要錯失良機啊！！<br />\n時間所剩不多<br />\n爭取一分一秒一卷 提升更多"},{"pid":"a7481aef1258c8707396cb0d0265e52e4b952d08","tid":145354,"uid":4427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:53:22.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227f9973ab9a69492c1549dec4eef383fcf9bdc3","tid":145354,"uid":17880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:58:26.000Z","msg":"正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a678f406db5eb93b3631e522940ca11290fb933","tid":145354,"uid":89462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"岩岩做完份MC. 幾似DSE，不過深少少<br />\n利申：40/45 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df89d0fdde115f8eb6967d8c3c258f3ad990987","tid":145354,"uid":17880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩做完份MC. 幾似DSE，不過深少少<br />\n利申：40/45 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i